= SDL_GetTextureAlphaMod =
Use this function to get the additional alpha value used in render copy operations.


== Syntax ==
```c++
int SDL_GetTextureAlphaMod(SDL_TextureID textureID,
                           Uint8*        alpha)
```

== Function Parameters ==
{|
|'''textureID'''
|the texture to query
|-
|'''alpha'''
|a pointer filled in with the source alpha value
|}

== Return Value ==
Returns 0 on success or -1 if the texture is not valid; call [[SDL_GetError]]() for more information.

